charts.description:
For infants (children < 1 year), the number of HIV positive tests, PLHIV newly on ART and PLHIV retained on treatment for 12 months, over the past 3 months.
Monitoring HIV programme effectiveness for test and treat policy and retention on treatment over time among infants.
charts.name: HIV: HIV cascade < 1 years - last 3 months

charts.description:
